  m_Name: Guiding_Gust
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::AbilitySO
  abilityName: Guiding Gust
  description: "Ascend to the top of a vertical surface you are\ntouching, lifted
    on a burst of wind.\nPASSION - Joy\nRestore SPI when you deliver good news.\nTattered
    wing, loath'ed cry, born of ugly bill\nAnd yet what heights, what lofty sights,
    this skwarmew captures still\nGull Knight\nPATCHWORK ARMOUR\nSome taken from...
    Mixed with...\n1 Fallen soldiers Flexible leather\n2 Ancient tomb Sleek bronze\n3
    Shipwreck Polished steel\n4 A fighting pit Brass studs\n5 A defeated Knight Padded
    coat\n6 Thankful militia Thick furs\nKNIGHTED BY...\nThe Floating Seer\nVIG 12,
    CLA 12, SPI 14, 2 GD\n\u2022 A bloated bladder of a being, humming as\nshe bobs
    about in the air buoyantly,\nyelping as she hits the ceiling.\n\u2022 Sees through
    the eyes of all flying beings.\n\u2022 Wants to float free toward the stars.\nHates
    being confined. Being grounded\ncauses agony.\nPerson: Zealous student ~ Name:
    Foxter ~ Characteristic: Always alert\nObject: Crystal mead ~ Beast: Paradise
    cockerel ~ State: Searching ~ Theme: Ice\n5\n8\nThe"
